em-content" data-index="1" data-key="content1" style="padding-left: 45px"><div data-label="Text Block" id="e-1614761674524-2" class="element-wrap" data-id="1614761674524-2" style="display: block;"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-exc=""><p>Heat milk until lukewarm and transfer to a medium bowl and whisk in the yeast. Set aside for</p><p>later.</p></div></div></div></li><li style="margin-bottom: 4px"><span class="gf-il-icon item-content" data-index="2" data-key="content" style="width: 45px"><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" id="e-1678942740557" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1678942740557" style=""><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>02</p></div></div></span><div class="gf-il-content item-content" data-index="2" data-key="content1" style="padding-left: 45px"><div data-label="Text Block" id="e-1678942740577" class="element-wrap" data-id="1678942740577" style="display: block;"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-exc=""><p>In the bowl of an electric mixer, add self-raising flour, cinnamon, nutmeg, allspice, cloves, sugar</p><p>and salt, then mix to combine.</p></div></div></div></li><li style="margin-bottom: 4px"><span class="gf-il-icon item-content" data-index="3" data-key="content" style="width: 45px"><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" id="e-1678942750205" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1678942750205" style=""><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>03</p></div></div></span><div class="gf-il-content item-content" data-index="3" data-key="conten